message.entry: CPSELECT is not available on this platform.
CPSELECT expects 2 output arguments when WAIT is true.
CPSELECT expects 1 output argument when WAIT is false.
CPSELECT: CPSTRUCT must be a structure.
CPSELECT: Expected fifth input argument to be a string or a character vector.
CPSELECT: XYINPUT_IN and XYBASE_IN must be M-by-2.
Function CPSELECT expected an even number of parameter/value arguments.
The parameter, {0}, is not recognized by {1}
CPSELECT: {0} must be a grayscale image.
CPSELECT: {0} must be a valid image file.
